description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Ravens kicker Justin Tucker about his NFL record breaking Field Goal. Former Running Back and Rams Radio Analyst calls in to recap yesterday's win against the Bucs. And Carson Palmer discusses which type of film rookies QBs should not be watching.
